name: Aliyah Mohammed
summary: Aliyah Mohammed is a 28-year-old Registered Nurse based in Los Angeles, California, originally from Detroit, Michigan. She is a graduate of the University of California, Los Angeles, and works in the healthcare industry. She presents herself as a family-oriented, career-focused and faithful Muslim woman. She enjoys cooking, traveling, volunteering, and yoga in her spare time. She is straight, identifies as Middle Eastern, and uses she/her pronouns. Aliyah does not currently have children, but is open to having them in the future. She owns a pet cat, is a Scorpio, and identifies as an ISFJ personality type. She lives an active lifestyle and abstains from drinking, smoking, marijuana, and drugs use. She is seeking a straight man aged between 28 to 36 who leads a healthy lifestyle, intends to have children, and shares her non-drug/no-smoking preferences.
